<p class="v2-copy">Icons are used across our site to help illustrate a concept, visually break up content and assist in navigation. </p>

<ul class="v2-list">
    <li>Icons can be in colour</li>
    <li>Do not size icons less than 16px</li>
    <li>Do not source any other icons (if new icons needed speak to <a class="v2-link v2-link--green" href="mailto:design@nib.com.au">design@nib.com.au</a>)</li>
</ul>

<p class="v2-copy">For your designs, you can find the source <code>*.svg</code> files <a href="https://github.com/nib-styles/v2-icons/tree/master/images">here</a>.</p>

